<p><a href="#20">Open your own user account</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the tab <strong>Personal settings » Shortcuts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Set the shortcuts. Note <a href="#tabelle-shortcuts">Table 2</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
