<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item(s) below reorder level</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Shows which items need to be reordered. The items are listed according to their warehouse.<br>
